<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أخرجه البخاري <span class="c2">(١٢٥٤)</span> .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - حماد بن زيد عنه.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>البخاري <span class="c2">(١٢٥٨)</span> ، مسلم <span class="c2">(٣/٤٧)</span> ، ابن حبان <span class="c2">(٣٠٢١)</span> .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
